@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xcdibf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (0.37 + wp.cos(wp.sin(v1 + 0.12)))
    v2 = ((0.02 / wp.cos(v0 + 0.78)) / (v2 - tmp))
    tmp = wp.cos(0.65)
    v1 = 0.71
    v2 = v2
    v0 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
